def boxcar_matched_filter(data, width):
        filtered_data = []
    sum_val = sum(data[:width])
    filtered_data.append(sum_val)

        sum_val = sum_val - data[i-1] + data[i+width-1]
        filtered_data.append(sum_val)
    return filtered_data
